data.description: Fall in Love with this Remarkable, Circa 1900 Cape Cod in Downtown Canal Winchester! Cozy covered front porch, large living room with decorative fireplace, tall ceilings and hardwood floors, remodeled kitchen with granite counters, newer cabinetry, island and eating space, separate 1st floor laundry, updated bathrooms, second story loft, big fenced in backyard with patio and storage building, newer three dimensional roof & insulating windows. This charming home is close to great restaurants, breweries and shops in Downtown Canal Winchester!
